

VanillaJS DOM usage
-------------------
The last updates of ES5,6,7 make the javascript usable without additionnal libraries:

To see the usage in the general browser, use canIUse:
<https://caniuse.com/#search=queryselectorall>

Jquery like functions for Dom research: 

 - element.getElementById
 - document.querySelector
 - document.querySelectorAll
 - document.getElementsByTagName
 
sources
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document.querySelectorAll

<https://developer.mozilla.org/fr/docs/Web/API/Document>
<https://developer.mozilla.org/fr/docs/Web/API/Element>